docs.text:
Welcome to MkLorum


For full documentation visit 
mkdocs.org
.


Commands




mkdocs new [dir-name]
 - Create a new project.


mkdocs serve
 - Start the live-reloading docs server.


mkdocs build
 - Build the documentation site.


mkdocs help
 - Print this help message.




Project layout


mkdocs.yml    # The configuration file.
docs/
    index.md  # The documentation homepage.
    ...       # Other markdown pages, images and other files.

arma Scylla. Parat sacrata. Cum quamvis visuraque ut coniuge  bracchia  geminis,
et mentis sanguine pallenti nimbis permanet, os! Lacertos aeque  addita  nigra
comitantibus rostro levati tamen. Recentem duo ne viscera dixit rettulit sic
illa, vivit nomen digitos, ministerio fluviis.  Contigerant taurum utque et tuam! Non ac dixi Ladon fruge mirantibus disiunxisse
